thread.title: JLT Mobile Computers Q3 EBITDA swings to loss SEK 0.2 million
thread.title_full: BRIEF-JLT Mobile Computers Q3 EBITDA swings to loss SEK 0.2 million | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: JLT Mobile Computers Q3 EBITDA swings to loss SEK 0.2 million
text:
Oct 22 JLT Mobile Computers publ AB :
* Q3 net sales 16.1 million Swedish crowns ($1.9 million) versus 21.2 million crowns year ago
* Q3 EBITDA loss 0.2 million crowns versus profit 3.2 million crowns year ago
Source text for Eikon:
 ($1 = 8.3153 Swedish crowns) (Gdynia Newsroom)
